It's disgusting.

00:17:40.590 --> 00:17:43.360
Even the thought makes
me want to puke, sort of.

00:17:43.360 --> 00:17:45.280
So fresh spice is
the same thing.

00:17:45.280 --> 00:17:50.660
So if you get the grocery store
fresh spices-- tomatoes takes

00:17:50.660 --> 00:17:54.100
a lot of salt-- if you get the
grocery store fresh spices that

00:17:54.100 --> 00:17:56.650
are already ground,
they could be years old,

00:17:56.650 --> 00:17:58.450
just like if you got
pre-ground coffee.

00:17:58.450 --> 00:18:00.290
It could be-- you don't know
how old it is, necessarily,

00:18:00.290 --> 00:18:02.715
so you always get the whole
bean, freshly roasted, grind

00:18:02.715 --> 00:18:03.559
it yourself.

00:18:03.559 --> 00:18:05.600
Same thing with black
pepper, any sort of spices.

00:18:05.600 --> 00:18:07.880
It's totally, totally worth it.

