A little more black
pepper and a touch

00:20:09.900 --> 00:20:12.830
of salt. Don't be
afraid of salt.

00:20:12.830 --> 00:20:15.447
Just do not be afraid
of salt. It makes it

00:20:15.447 --> 00:20:17.030
so that you can
actually taste things.

00:20:17.030 --> 00:20:18.571
I mean, it's just
one of these things

00:20:18.571 --> 00:20:22.620
that if something's missing,
you're like, what's missing?

00:20:22.620 --> 00:20:25.680
Chances are it's the
salt. And what I want you

00:20:25.680 --> 00:20:28.047
to do--it's
mesmerizing isn't it?

00:20:28.047 --> 00:20:29.880
What I want you to get
in the habit of doing

00:20:29.880 --> 00:20:32.636
