say this gazpacho or something,

00:20:32.636 --> 00:20:34.950
and you're not
quite sure what it

00:20:34.950 --> 00:20:37.130
is that's missing,
what I want you to do

00:20:37.130 --> 00:20:40.580
is take a little spoon
like I did earlier,

00:20:40.580 --> 00:20:43.200
take the little spoon, and just
put a little bit of gazpacho

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:46.800
on it, and then add just
like a couple dots of salt.

00:20:46.800 --> 00:20:49.830
Once you add the salt to this
giant thing, you're done.

00:20:49.830 --> 00:20:51.200
Maybe it needed acid.

