And then up here on
my left-hand side,

00:35:33.850 --> 00:35:39.610
I do have the pine nuts
that we had toasted earlier.

00:35:39.610 --> 00:35:42.080
And then how I toast my pine
nuts, and all nuts, in fact,

00:35:42.080 --> 00:35:45.850
is in your cookbook that you
have in front of you right now.

00:35:45.850 --> 00:35:46.660
Pine nuts.

00:35:46.660 --> 00:35:49.411
They come from pine trees,
from freaking pine cones.

00:35:49.411 --> 00:35:51.660
They are expensive, and
