you would just shave
some over the top,

00:37:44.395 --> 00:37:47.130
because that's really sexy, and
it's just beautiful big pieces

00:37:47.130 --> 00:37:49.210
of Parmesan.

00:37:49.210 --> 00:37:50.970
And that's the second dish.

